5.15.24  10:52 pm   you know the difference between a plot twist and a cliffhanger

      sure. a plot twist is where the plot takes an unexpected turn. a cliffhanger is when the there is a break in the story (such as the end of a chapter or the end of an episode) and something has just happened that leaves you hanging in a state of utmost curiosity over what may happen in the next section
